il.technion.ewolf.kbr.concurrent

クラス DummyFuture<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.technion.ewolf.kbr.concurrent.DummyFuture<T>
  • 型パラメータ:
    T - any arbitrary result type
    すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.util.concurrent.Future<T>

    public class DummyFuture<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Future<T>
    A future initiated with the result This class is used to mock future when we already have the results but need to return a future. One example is result found in cache.
